## File Structure (Proposed)

```
Mental-Health-Detection-ML/
├── system2/
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── config.py              # Feature list, population norms, prototype vectors
│   ├── baseline_screener.py   # 3-gate baseline screening (Phase 1)
│   ├── prototype_matcher.py   # Distance scoring engine (Phase 2)
│   ├── temporal_validator.py  # Temporal shape validation (Phase 3)
│   ├── life_event_filter.py   # Life event filter (Phase 4)
│   ├── explainability.py      # Output formatting + radar chart (Phase 5)
│   ├── pipeline.py            # Full S2 pipeline orchestrator (Phase 6)
│   └── tests/
│       ├── test_screener.py
│       ├── test_matcher.py
│       ├── test_temporal.py
│       └── test_pipeline.py
├── data/
│   └── population_norms.json  # Phase 0 output
├── metric_based_system2.md    # Design doc (already done ✅)
└── system1.py                 # S1 (other team)
```
